data.description: Welcome home to this lovely well maintained ranch in the Rolling Green neighborhood. Freshly painted with lots of natural light coming through the wall of windows in the living area. Open floor plan leads to the kitchen and spacious dining area, perfect for family gatherings. The large picture window in the dining room overlooks the fenced in backyard. Nice landscaping with an abundance of colorful perennials to look forward to the the spring and summer. Three bedrooms on the main floor with the fourth large bedroom and walk in closet in the newly finished lower level. This home has many updates including new windows, rain gutters and new leaf guards installed in 2022. Mechanicals are in great condition with a newer furnace and central air unit. Above ground pool with heater is two years old, making the backyard patio the place to be. New solar panels keep the cost of electric low. Centrally located. Close to shopping with Elementary and Jr. High schools just a short walk away. Don't miss out, schedule your showing today!
